Tilemaps -  https://youtu.be/otQH2M-Lkd0?si=acExNSU1Zvn1Fylf https://learn.unity.com/tutorial/introduction-to-tilemaps
consists of a grid overlay and a number of other components working
together. The entire system allows you to paint levels using tiles and brush tools
and define rules for how tiles behave.

